data.description: Discover the charm of this cozy home with a split bedroom layout. It has a welcoming front porch and high vaulted ceilings that create a spacious feel. The master suite is comfortable with dual closets and a lovely trey ceiling. Relax in the master bath's jetted tub. Every room has 2” blinds and ceiling fans for your comfort. Outside, there's a peaceful deck overlooking the private backyard. This home is low-maintenance and move-in ready, perfect for simple living. You'll benefit from low county taxes, great schools, and the opportunity for 100% USDA financing with $0 down payment, making homeownership easier.
